9:21 AM Defendant KENJALA S JOHNSON appeared by video.  Attorney Matthew Steven McElroy in court for State of Wisconsin. Defendant has no objection to holding this hearing by zoom. Defendant confirms receipt of the criminal complaint and waives reading. Court instructs the defendant of the maximum penalty on each count. Court sets bond at $500 signature bond and conditions of: Defendant is to complete processing with the Green Lake County Sheriff's Department.  Court grants defendant until October 4, 2022 to complete processing and sign the bond. Court instructs defendant regarding his/her right to a preliminary hearing. Defendant waives the time limits. Court will set for Status of Counsel October 4, 2022 at 3:15 PM. Mandatory Appearance. Court quashes warrant.
